 KoRn 与 Adidas Originals 联手推出第二次服装合作https://www.nme.com/news/music/korn-and-adidas-originals-team-up-for-second-clothing-collab-3755001?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=korn-and-adidas-originals-联手打造第二套服装Anagricel DuranThu, 09 May 2024 20:45:31 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalNu-metal https://www.nme.com/?p=3755001 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="科恩 x 阿迪达斯。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该合作计划将于 5 月 15 日发布</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/korn-and-adidas-originals-team-up-for-second-clothing-collab-3755001">KoRn 和 Adidas Originals 联手打造的第二款服装联名</a>系列首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="科恩 x 阿迪达斯。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artist/korn">KoRn</a>与 Adidas Originals 展开第二次服装合作。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/korn-requiem-nu-metal-start-the-healing-3155810">科恩：“在这张专辑中，我们的情感成长了。音乐可以治愈我们所有人”</a></strong></li></ul><p>去年，新金属传奇人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/korn-are-finally-partnering-with-adidas-for-sneakers-collab-3475445">与运动服装品牌合作</a>，发布了两双运动鞋——Campus 00s 和 Supermodified——以及七件服装。</p><p>现在，两人再次合作推出该运动服饰品牌的第二款新品，该系列将于 5 月 15 日<a href="https://www.kornwebstore.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在网上</a>和指定商店上市。</p><p>该服装将采用带有联合品牌细节的绿色亮片运动服，为 Korn 网上商店独家提供。袖子上印有阿迪达斯三条纹图案的长袖 T 恤、三双袜子以及带有 KoRn 标志和三条纹细节的帽子也将可供购买。 </p><figure id="attachment_3755009" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3755009" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3755009" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-X-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="科恩 X 阿迪达斯。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-X-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-X-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-X-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-X-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-X-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Korn-X-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3755009" class="wp-caption-text">科恩 X 阿迪达斯。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>一双新的运动鞋将推出 Campus 2 款式以及 Supermodified 运动鞋。厚实的 Campus 2 运动鞋采用毛茸茸的绒面革鞋面和隐藏式 KoRn 细节，而 KoRn 网店独家的 Supermodified 鞋型则采用醒目的亮绿色装饰。</p><p>两款运动鞋的配色均借鉴了《Follow the Leader》专辑周期期间发布的广受欢迎的复古 KoRn T 恤的美学规范。这两款运动鞋都将配备一套独特的配件，包括图案鞋垫、多种配色的备用鞋带、一套粗鞋带、一套四张贴纸、吉他拨片钥匙扣和联名旅行风格盒子。</p><p> 1997 年，乐队发行了歌曲“ADIDAS”，似乎是在利用品牌名称代表“我整天都梦想着性”的神话。 </p><figure id="attachment_3755010" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3755010" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3755010" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/KoRn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="科恩 x 阿迪达斯。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/KoRn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/KoRn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/KoRn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/KoRn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/KoRn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/KoRn-x-Adidas.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3755010" class="wp-caption-text">科恩 x 阿迪达斯。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>2021 年<a href="https://www.kerrang.com/it-was-about-smashing-down-walls-how-adidas-invaded-nu-metal" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Kerrang 采访！</em></a> KoRn 主唱乔纳森·戴维斯 (Jonathan Davis) 表示，他对运动装的喜爱是“打破常规”。 “这是关于打破墙壁并拥抱各种不同的音乐风格和音乐文化。它违背了金属应有的一切。”</p><p>这位主唱还解释说，尽管该品牌提供了一些免费商品，但据报道该公司并未开放商业交易。</p><p>他们与竞争对手 Puma 合作。 “我们转而选择 Puma，因为他们告诉我们，他们会让我们参与广告，并给我们一点钱让我们穿他们的衣服，”戴维斯说。 “我们当时就想，‘操，是的！这比阿迪达斯为我们所做的还要多！”这不是卖光的事情。这是关于尊重。”</p><p>今年早些时候，戴维斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/korns-jonathan-davis-reflects-on-immature-song-a-d-i-d-a-s-youre-24-years-old-sex-is-all-you-really-think-about-3567187">公开了乐队的歌曲“ADIDAS”，并反思了这首歌的“不成熟”含义</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/korn-and-adidas-originals-team-up-for-second-clothing-collab-3755001">KoRn 和 Adidas Originals 联手打造的第二款服装联名</a>系列首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
